data.description: Welcome home to country living at 25410 Rolling Hills Dr, one of the largest lots in Country Lane Estates!   This serene property beckons those seeking a canvas to customize their living space. Whether renovating the existing mobile home with some TLC, expanding it, or constructing a new dream home, the potential is endless on this sprawling 4-acre plot. Adding to the appeal are two sheds with full electricity, perfect for storage or as workspaces. There is plenty of room for horses or gardening! The possibilities are endless! A low tax rate and low HOA add to the desirability of the property, just ready for you to call home! Contact us today to schedule your private tour!
